&lt;h3&gt;Duration&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The length of this apprenticeship will usually be a minimum of 24 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are no prerequisite qualifications for this apprenticeship, although apprentices without level 2 English and Mathematics will need to achieve this level prior to taking the end point assessment. Individual employers may also have entry requirements in place for roles offered in addition to those specified in this document.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Level&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a Level 4 Apprenticeship&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Review Date&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3 years or when significant change is required&lt;/p&gt;
